---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About PetFoodLab">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About PetFoodLab</h1>
  
  <div class="prose lg:prose-xl">
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
      We're on a mission to help pet owners make informed decisions about pet food.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Story</h2>
    <p>
      PetFoodLab was founded in 2026 by pet owners who were frustrated by the lack of 
      honest, science-backed pet food reviews. Too many sites are influenced by 
      manufacturer partnerships or affiliate commissions.
    </p>
    <p>
      We take a different approach: every review is based on ingredient analysis, 
      nutritional science, and real customer feedback.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Review Process</h2>
    <ol>
      <li><strong>Ingredient Analysis:</strong> We evaluate every ingredient for quality and safety</li>
      <li><strong>Nutritional Completeness:</strong> We verify AAFCO compliance</li>
      <li><strong>Customer Feedback:</strong> We analyze thousands of verified reviews</li>
      <li><strong>Value Assessment:</strong> We calculate price per serving for fair comparisons</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>Our Promise</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>✅ Independent reviews - we buy products ourselves</li>
      <li>✅ No manufacturer influence</li>
      <li>✅ Transparent affiliate disclosure</li>
      <li>✅ Science-backed recommendations</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
      Have questions or suggestions? Reach out at 
      <a href="mailto:hello@petfoodlab.it.com" class="text-blue-600">hello@petfoodlab.it.com</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
